README for .../gallery/2dprob/problem.04/figures/fig2

This is the only figure that was taken directly from the version 3.5 website, and not regenerated with the most recent version of dzeus36.  It was creating a fair bit of consternation with Logan (who was hired at the time to update much of the content for the new website), and it didn't seem worth it to try to reproduce this particular figure.  Other than more proportionate-looking x-annotations, it wouldn't look any different once done.

DAC, May 2016.
